[20260424-095049.9606]  
[20260424-095049.9607]  Converts from some bases to a wide variety of others. Strictly positional
[20260424-095049.9623]  notation conversion, not for binary-to-text encoding/decoding. (Though you
[20260424-095049.9640]  can use the same common 2^N encoding bases as positional notation.)
